        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-54" parent="0" value="Annotations" />
        <mxCell id="3rJstIUwe-mpcvYpoVB0-90" parent="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-54" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;shadow=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=2;" value="&lt;b&gt;3. &lt;/b&gt;ed25519 keypair created specifically for this deployment." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="180" x="-420" y="770" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="3rJstIUwe-mpcvYpoVB0-65" parent="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-54" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;shadow=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=2;" value="&lt;b&gt;2. &lt;/b&gt;ETH withdrawn to a non-custodial wallet address." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="160" x="230" y="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="3rJstIUwe-mpcvYpoVB0-99" parent="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-54" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;shadow=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=2;" value="&lt;b&gt;10. &lt;/b&gt;Full balance of deployer&#39;s LP tokens are burned." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="46" width="170" x="-430" y="550" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="3rJstIUwe-mpcvYpoVB0-100" parent="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-54" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;shadow=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=2;" value="&lt;b&gt;4. &lt;/b&gt;Deployer wallet funded with ETH for backing liquidity &amp;amp; gas fees." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="150" x="-20" y="340" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="3rJstIUwe-mpcvYpoVB0-64" parent="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-54" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;shadow=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=2;" value="&lt;b&gt;1. &lt;/b&gt;Money sent to an exchange to purchase ETH-on-Base.&amp;nbsp;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="170" x="490" y="390" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-61" parent="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-54" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;shadow=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=2;" value="&lt;b&gt;5. &lt;/b&gt;Tokin&#39; ERC-20 contract deployed on Base blockchain from deployer&#39;s address. The new token&#39;s address is needed to seed the liquidity pool." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="90" width="170" x="-150" y="430" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-62" parent="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-54" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;shadow=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=2;" value="&lt;b&gt;6. &lt;/b&gt;Tokin&#39;s constructor is invoked, causing the full supply to be minted into the deployer&#39;s balance." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="70" width="170" x="-340" y="-170" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-63" parent="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-54" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;shadow=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=2;" value="&lt;b&gt;8. &lt;/b&gt;A new liquidity pool is seeded using the deployer&#39;s entire TOKIN balance and an amount of ETH (deposited as Wrapped ETH), serving as the swap pairing and defining the new token&#39;s value. An amount of the pool&#39;s liquidity provider (LP) token is minted to the deployer in exchange." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="240" x="-980" y="650" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-64" parent="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-54" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;shadow=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=2;" value="&lt;b&gt;9. &lt;/b&gt;The address of the new TOKIN:WETH pool (== LP ERC-20 token) is fetched for subsequent LP token burning." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="72.5" width="170" x="-870" y="420" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-65" parent="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-54" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;shadow=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=2;" value="&lt;b&gt;11. &lt;/b&gt;An ETH/TOKIN swap is routed through the new pool to purchase a &quot;souvenir&quot; amount of Tokin&#39; as a regular trader. The swap action is preceded by the generation of a &quot;quote&quot; to ascertain the expected amount of TOKIN in exchange for a given amount of ETH and to set a slippage floor for the trade." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="110" width="260" x="-1440" y="420" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-67" parent="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-54" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;shadow=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=2;" value="&lt;b&gt;7.&lt;/b&gt; The&lt;b&gt; &lt;/b&gt;full balance of deployer&#39;s TOKIN is approved for transfer by the Aerodrome router." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="72.5" width="140" x="-415" y="417.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-71" parent="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-54" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;shadow=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=2;" value="&lt;b&gt;12. &lt;/b&gt;The first swap routed through the TOKIN:WETH pool prompts public indexers to begin tracking the price and transaction history at the new pool address." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="82.5" width="200" x="-730" y="-100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-73" parent="N1oQfP46GQ1lDOvrroKS-54" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;shadow=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=2;" value="&lt;b&gt;13. &lt;/b&gt;Once all deployer activity has been completed (including contract source code verification, metadata configuration on various wallet / DEX platforms, etc.), the deployer wallet can be destroyed." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="90" width="240" x="-720" y="770" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
